@startuml
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
boundary "Customer" as C
participant "Warehouse Staff" as WS
participant "Driver" as D
entity "Dispatcher" as D2
D2 -> WS : Load Package
note over WS : processing load package
D --> C : Schedule Pickup
WS -> C : Report Issue
note over C : processing report issue
C ->> D2 : Fuel Vehicle
activate D2
D2 --> C : ACK
deactivate D2
@enduml